<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-10-12T06:05:14-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-10-12T06:05:14-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-12T06:05:14-04:00</updated><title> X为欧盟指控其散布以色列与哈马斯战争虚假信息而进行辩护</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 X 徽标叠加在 Twitter 徽标上的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HImy4MQ5IIevHGyLyqsVI_ZhCbA=/0x0:3001x2001/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72747279/STK160_X_Twitter_002.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;xejfP9&quot;>;X 首席执行官 Linda Yaccarino 表示在哈马斯对以色列发动恐怖袭击后，前身为 Twitter 的社交媒体平台已识别并删除了“数百个”哈马斯附属帐户，并“采取行动删除或标记了数万条内容”。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/lindayaX/status/1712342353304846603&quot;>;Yaccarino 的信&lt;/a>;是为了回应 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ThierryBreton/status/1711808891757944866&quot;>;欧盟委员蒂埃里·布雷顿 (Thierry Breton) 担心 X 被用来“传播非法内容和虚假信息”，这可能违反了欧盟严格的新数字服务法案 (DSA)。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;b2X03J&quot;>;X 与欧盟之间的来回争执正值欧盟实施 DSA 之际，该法案规定大型在线平台有义务删除非法内容并减轻公共安全风险...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23914020/x-twitter-israel-hamas-war-disinformation-misinformation-european-union -dsa-commissioner&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23914020/x-twitter-israel-hamas-war-disinformation-misinformation-european-union-dsa-commissioner" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23914020/x-twitter-israel-hamas-war-disinformation-misinformation-european-union-dsa-commissioner</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-12T00:23:06-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-12T00:23:06-04:00</updated><title>您仍然可以抓住的最佳 Pr